'''Ayimagonu afahyɛ''' yɛ afehyia [[afahyɛ]] a ahenfo ne wɔn manfo a wɔn wɔ Dafo a ɛwɔ Tongu Atitif fam no di.<ref>https://www.peacefmonline.com/pages/local/social/201711/336698.php</ref><ref>https://www.todaygh.com/work-to-begin-on-dorfor-road/</ref><ref name="ghanaemberlin.de">https://ghanaemberlin.de/travel-tourism/festival/</ref> Ɛne Juapon yɛ bɛyɛ Kilometa kakrabi wɔ Frao Mantam no wɔ Ghana<ref name="ghanaemberlin.de"/><ref>https://visitvoltaregion.com/about-volta/</ref>. Wodi saa afahyɛ no wɔ bosome a ɛtɔ so du baako no mu<ref name="touringghana.com">https://touringghana.com/volta-region/</ref><ref>https://www.easytrackghana.com/cultural-overview-ghana-festivals.php</ref>.

== Afa hyɛ ==
Ahenfo no bɔ dwa data wɔ afahyɛ no bere so<ref name="ghanaemberlin.de"/>. Nneɛma ahorɔw a wɔyɛ ne nsguo, ahenfo a wɔtenatena wɔn apakan mu a wɔn manfoɔ de nnwomtoɔ ne asaw die di wɔn akyi. Wɔyɛ oyikyerɛ wɔ ntaadehyɛ mu. Ahenfo no nso tena wɔn agua mu ma wɔn manfo besraa won<ref name="touringghana.com"/><ref>https://www.fiandadghanalimited.com/ayimagonu-festival/</ref>.

